@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_soxial(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v0 = v0
    v1 = tmp
    v0 = (v0 * 0.56)
    v1 = (((v2 + 0.56 * v1 + 0.20) * (v0 + 0.39 / v1 + 0.52)) / 0.75)
    tmp = (0.76 / ((tmp + 1.00 - v0 + 0.01) * 0.79))
    tmp = v0
    v2 = ((wp.sin(tmp + 0.75) - (tmp + 0.07 + v1 + 0.49)) * wp.sin((tmp + 0.88 / v0 + 0.90)))
    data[tid] = v0
